  <original-body>text_area_tag('item[description]') should return:

 &lt;textarea id=&quot;item_description&quot; name=&quot;item[description]&quot;&gt;&lt;/textarea&gt;

 instead of:

 &lt;textarea id=&quot;item[description]&quot; name=&quot;item[description]&quot;&gt;&lt;/textarea&gt;

